OL,3,CCouncil accountant jailed for five
OL,4,Cyears for stealing #1,000,000
OL,6,FA council accountant has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor five years for stealing almost
OL,8,F#1,000,000 from his employer.
OL,10,FAlan Doig, 57, stole from Gedling
OL,11,FBorough Council in Nottinghamshire for
OL,12,Falmost two decades.
OL,14,FHe made 86 fraudulent transactions and
OL,15,Fhe used the money to fund his gambling
OL,16,Faddiction.
OL,18,FDoig started making fraudulent
OL,19,Fpayments in 2003.
