OL,6,FIt said: "He (Doig) was an expert and
OL,7,Fused his position to abuse the system.
OL,8,FThe money he stole would have been 6%
OL,9,Fof the council's 2024-2025 budget.
OL,10,FThis has had an impact on every single
OL,11,Fresident in the borough.
OL,13,F"On an average of more than #46,000
OL,14,Fper annum, that could have employed
OL,15,Fextra street cleaners, bin collectors
OL,16,For gardeners who would have made a
OL,17,Freal difference to the borough."
