OL,13,Fincident and that they would recover
OL,14,Fall the money he stole.
OL,16,FMark Kennedy from the Crown
OL,17,FProsecution Service said: "Doig knew
OL,18,Fthe systems at his workplace and
OL,19,Favoided detection over many years.
